@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Privacy Policy";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>@ViewBag.Title - Starluxe Cinema</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/privacy.css" />
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Прожектори -->
    <div class="spotlight left"></div>
    <div class="spotlight right"></div>

    <!-- Overlay със съдържание -->
    <div class="overlay">
        <h1 class="cinema-title fade-in delay-1">Privacy Policy</h1>

        <p class="fade-in delay-2">Welcome to <strong style="color:#d6a94d;">Starluxe Cinema</strong>. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our website.</p>
        <p class="fade-in delay-3">This is a personal project, and we aim to respect your privacy while keeping things simple and transparent.</p>

        <h2 class="fade-in delay-4">1. What We Collect</h2>
        <ul class="fade-in delay-5">
            <li>
                <strong>Voluntarily Provided Data</strong><br />
                If you contact us, submit a form, or sign up for a newsletter (if available), we may collect:
                <ul>
                    <li>Your name</li>
                    <li>Email address</li>
                    <li>Any message or feedback you provide</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Automatic Data (via standard analytics tools)</strong><br />
                Like most websites, we may use tools such as Google Analytics to collect:
                <ul>
                    <li>Browser type, device info, and operating system</li>
                    <li>IP address and approximate location</li>
                    <li>Pages visited and time spent on the site</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="fade-in delay-4">2. How We Use the Data</h2>
        <ul class="fade-in delay-5">
            <li>Respond to your messages or inquiries</li>
            <li>Improve the website and content</li>
            <li>Understand usage patterns and traffic sources</li>
            <li>Optionally, send you updates (only if you’ve opted in)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="fade-in delay-4">3. Cookies</h2>
        <p class="fade-in delay-5">We may use cookies for basic site functionality and analytics. You can control or disable cookies via your browser settings.</p>

        <h2 class="fade-in delay-4">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p class="fade-in delay-5">We may use third-party services like Google Analytics and email providers. These services may collect data as described in their own privacy policies.</p>

        <h2 class="fade-in delay-4">5. Data Sharing</h2>
        <p class="fade-in delay-5">We do <strong>not</strong> sell or share your personal information with third parties for marketing.</p>

        <h2 class="fade-in delay-4">6. Your Rights</h2>
        <ul class="fade-in delay-5">
            <li>Request to view, update, or delete your personal data</li>
            <li>Unsubscribe from email communications</li>
            <li>Contact us if you have privacy questions</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="fade-in delay-4">7. Children’s Privacy</h2>
        <p class="fade-in delay-5">This site is not intended for children under 13. We don’t knowingly collect data from minors.</p>

        <h2 class="fade-in delay-4">8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p class="fade-in delay-5">We may update this policy as the project evolves. Any changes will be posted here with a new effective date.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>